<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>The Feast Express</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Grey+Qo&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header
      style="color: #aff4eb"
      class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-md-between py-3"
    >
      <div class="col-md-3 mb-2 mb-md-0 ml-2">
        <img
          src="/images/burger.svg"
          alt="Example Icon"
          style="
            height: 50px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            border: 2px solid white;
            border-radius: 30%;
            padding: 6px;
          "
        />
      </div>

      <ul class="nav col-12 col-md-auto mb-2 justify-content-center mb-md-0">
        <li>
          <a style="color: white" href="/" class="nav-link px-2">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            style="background-color: transparent; color: white"
            href="/order"
            class="nav-link px-2"
            >Order Food</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            style="background-color: transparent; color: white"
            href="/checkout"
            class="nav-link px-2"
            >Checkout</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="col-md-3 text-end">
        <button
          type="button"
          class="btn btn-outline-light me-2 loginHover login"
        >
          <a style="text-decoration: none" href="/login">Login</a>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light me-2">
          <a style="text-decoration: none" href="/signup">Sign-up</a>
        </button>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main>
      <h1
        style="
          text-align: center;
          font-style: italic;
          color: white;
          font-family: Grey Qo, cursive;
          font-weight: 400;
          font-style: normal;
          font-size: 5rem;
        "
      >
        The Feast Express
      </h1>
      <div class="px-4 pt-5 my-5 text-center">
        <h2 style="color: white" class="display-4 fw-bold text-body-emphasis">
          Unmatched Flavor Fusion
        </h2>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
          <p class="lead mb-4" style="color: white">
            Experience a culinary adventure with our fast food offerings that
            boast a rich, complex blend of flavors. We take pride in our unique
            recipes that combine traditional favorites with innovative twists.
            From our perfectly seasoned fries that burst with savory goodness to
            our juicy, flame-grilled burgers topped with gourmet ingredients,
            each bite promises an explosion of taste. Our commitment to using
            high-quality, fresh ingredients ensures that every dish is not only
            delicious but also packed with flavor, satisfying even the most
            discerning palate.
          </p>
          <div
            class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center mb-5"
          ></div>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 30vh">
          <div class="container px-5">
            <img
              src="/images/firstimage.jpg"
              class="img-fluid border rounded-3 shadow-lg mb-4"
              alt="Example image"
              width="700"
              height="700"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="color: white" class="px-4 pt-5 my-5 text-center">
        <h2 style="color: white" class="display-4 fw-bold text-body-emphasis">
          Speed and Convenience
        </h2>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
          <p class="lead mb-4" style="color: white">
            At the heart of our service is the promise of efficiency without
            compromising quality. We understand the fast-paced lives of our
            customers, which is why we’ve streamlined our operations to ensure
            quick, reliable service. Our state-of-the-art kitchen technology and
            trained staff work in harmony to prepare your meal promptly. Whether
            you're dining in, picking up, or opting for delivery, you can count
            on us to get your food to you hot and ready, making your experience
            seamless and satisfying.
          </p>
          <div
            class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center mb-5"
          ></div>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 30vh">
          <div class="container px-5">
            <img
              src="/images/secondimage.jpg"
              class="img-fluid border rounded-3 shadow-lg mb-4"
              alt="Example image"
              width="700"
              height="700"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="px-4 pt-5 my-5 text-center">
        <h2 style="color: white" class="display-4 fw-bold text-body-emphasis">
          Commitment to Sustainability
        </h2>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
          <p class="lead mb-4" style="color: white">
            We believe that enjoying great food shouldn’t come at the expense of
            the environment. Our commitment to sustainability is reflected in
            every aspect of our operations. From sourcing ingredients locally to
            reduce our carbon footprint to using eco-friendly packaging, we’re
            dedicated to making a positive impact. We also prioritize waste
            reduction by implementing rigorous recycling and composting
            programs. By choosing us, you’re not only indulging in delicious
            fast food but also supporting a brand that cares about the planet.
          </p>
          <div
            class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center mb-5"
          ></div>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 30vh">
          <div class="container px-5">
            <img
              src="/images/thirdimage.jpg"
              class="img-fluid border rounded-3 shadow-lg mb-4"
              alt="Example image"
              width="700"
              height="700"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide">
          <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide-to="0"
              class="active"
              aria-current="true"
              aria-label="Slide 1"
            ></button>
            <button
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide-to="1"
              aria-label="Slide 2"
            ></button>
            <button
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide-to="2"
              aria-label="Slide 3"
            ></button>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <img
                src="/images/firstslider.jpg"
                class="d-block w-100"
                alt="..."
              />
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>First slide label</h5>
                <p>
                  Some representative placeholder content for the first slide.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img
                src="/images/secondslider.jpg"
                class="d-block w-100"
                alt="..."
              />
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Second slide label</h5>
                <p>
                  Some representative placeholder content for the second slide.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img
                src="/images/thirdslider.jpg"
                class="d-block w-100"
                alt="..."
              />
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Third slide label</h5>
                <p>
                  Some representative placeholder content for the third slide.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button
            class="carousel-control-prev"
            type="button"
            data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
            data-bs-slide="prev"
          >
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
          </button>
          <button
            class="carousel-control-next"
            type="button"
            data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
            data-bs-slide="next"
          >
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="py-3 my-4">
      <ul class="nav justify-content-center border-bottom pb-3 mb-3">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a
            style="color: white"
            href="/"
            class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary"
            >Home</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a
            style="color: white"
            href="/order"
            class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary"
            >Order Food</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a
            style="color: white"
            href="/checkout"
            class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary"
            >Checkout</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color: wheat" class="text-center text-body-secondary">
        © 2024 Company, Inc
      </p>
    </footer>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
